Document: PhysicalBoneSimulator3D  
Path: godot/classes/class_physicalbonesimulator3d.rst  
Summary: Methods for managing physics simulation and collision exceptions in PhysicalBoneSimulator3D.  

- is_simulating_physics (bool): const. No parameters.  
- physical_bones_add_collision_exception (void): Adds a collision exception. Parameters: exception (RID).  
- physical_bones_remove_collision_exception (void): Removes a collision exception. Parameters: exception (RID).  
- physical_bones_start_simulation (void): Starts simulation. Parameters: bones (Array<StringName>) with default value of empty array.  
- physical_bones_stop_simulation (void): Stops simulation. No parameters.
